title: Indie Electronic Playlist 1.0
description:
I listen to the Indie Rock Playlist, which is good, but I am interested in something a little more 'electronic'.  so that's what this is.  I use the term indie and electronic both VERY loosely... 

There's a mix of electro, indie pop, synth pop, indietronica, electronica and some fun stuff at the end. Hope you enjoy these lovely songs... 

Let me know if you like this!
